Package net.llamaslayers.minecraft.banana.gen.populators

Class Summary
BoatPopulator Boats.
BoulderPopulator Generates boulders for the foot of a mountain
BuildingPopulator Populates using BO2 files.
CavePopulator BlockPopulator for snake-based caves.
DesertPopulator BlockPopulator that turns deserts into sand and places cacti.
DungeonPopulator A BlockPopulator that places dungeons around the map.
FlowerPopulator BlockPopulator that places yellow flowers, red roses, and tall grass.
GlowstonePopulator Edited for BananaGen.
LakePopulator BlockPopulator that generates lava lakes.
MushroomPopulator BlockPopulator that generates giant mushrooms in tundra and taiga, a la Minecraft 1.8.
OrePopulator Populates the world with ores.
PalmTreePopulator Generate palm trees, like those one would find on a beach .
QuarryPopulator BlockPopulator that generates stone quarries.
RuinsPopulator Populator from BananaMaze to make crumbling walls.
RuinsPopulator2 Builds ruins.
SchematicPopulator Populates using .schematic files.
ShipwreckPopulator  
SnowPopulator BlockPopulator that coats tundra and taiga with snow.
SpookyRoomPopulator BlockPopulator that generates rooms made of nether materials, spider webs, and monster spawners.
StreetlightPopulator  
TorchPopulator Populator from BananaMaze to place torches on random surfaces.
TreePopulator BlockPopulator that adds trees based on the biome.
